title: Cucumber, Avocado, and Feta Salad
directions: In a large bowl, combine cucumber, avocado, lemon juice, feta, and dill. Gently stir to combine. Season with salt and black pepper, to taste. Serve.
Note-this salad is best the day it is made.
ingredients: 3 large avocados pit removed and chopped
Salt and black pepper to taste
